    Scope and Contents
Reports, planning documents, and budget requests prepared by the Planning Development Division and the Office of Institutional Research, 1970- .  Documents include building specifications for the Library, President's residence, Laboratory Office Building, land acquisition, perimeter road and parking lots, as well as other Phase I and Phase 'B'  plans.  Other documents: budget requests, long-range development plans, FCC applications for television station, and CONVOCOM agreement.
These files may be from John Takeuchi, University Architect.  
  
